ifsf_cmpnad.pro


top ifsf_cmpnad

IFSFIT

result = ifsf_cmpnad(wave, pars)

Compute Na D profile.

Return value

Flat spectrum Na D absorption included.

Parameters

wave in required type=dblarr(N)

Wavelength array over which to compute profile.

pars in required type=dblarr(4)

Parameters of profile: covering factor, optical depth, central wavelength, and Doppler parameter (in km/s)
